Chemfix Technologies Inc said itacquired the remaining 50 pct of its California affiliate,VenVirotek, previously owned by a Ventura, Calif. businessman.    Terms were not disclosed.    VenVirotek proved the Chemfix Process could be successfullyapplied to convert spent drilling fluids into a reusableclay-like product that is suitable for use as landfill cover. Reuter&#3;